    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_notes_f7f010b78016aeebd76e56d9283eb67f_112_8",
    "text": "B): We cannot ignore the fact that industrialization brings with it the probems of pollution. To solve these problems, we can start by educating the public about the hazards of pollution. The goverment on its pait should also design strictet laws to promote a deaner enviroment.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
